Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 全世界的少男少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你们也有准时收看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又到了JUDATV的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤机关的坏人又欺负我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提一点反对意见就被骂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他们作对的话会被带去可怕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有言论自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说这种纸扇也要被禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们真是渣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸扇是我的爱与灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.48,0:00:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗绊他们总是那么好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能看这种节目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.21,0:00:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JUDATV播出的时候没法换频道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤机关的确很强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有许多ARMA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.38,0:00:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以全世界的国家都对他们唯命是从
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许听信了服从他们就停止战争的言论
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道他们什么时候会出尔反尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们JUDA可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早以前就豁出性命在和加藤机关作战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中有人因为好友被加藤机关所杀才加入JUDA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是笨手笨脚的外行人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.92,0:01:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉中成长起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在最前线战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回过神来时 我们已经被他超过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让他独自出风头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也会努力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家助一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊的节目到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤机关
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我玩玩吧 孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是免了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中断播出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯绊 收工
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DECEIVE撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 真不带劲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地赶来 太扫兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 远藤兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟 快看这是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳槽去给儿童电视台做保镖了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有自己知道自己的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定会向世界证明JUDA的正当性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前我们可不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第18话 牢记死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么矢岛要这样对我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里面是鄂霍次克海的岛屿资料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该曾是俄罗斯的核潜艇基地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 我也想立刻就去营救城崎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在的JUDA里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在前线作战的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果傻乎乎的中招
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴的是加藤机关
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早濑在说人话!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 这么聪明的浩一不是浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 真的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是矢岛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会加害城崎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得相信?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在是加藤机关的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被上面命令的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城崎也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢岛不会做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能做…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢岛总是保护着我和浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个加藤机关不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那巨大的机器人和矢岛的右手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及打伤降矢的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢岛在加藤机关成为了那台MACHINA的因子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因子?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因子是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一也驾驶同样的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一突然变强也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没告诉她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我啊 为什么矢岛会那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢岛是为了理沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一 说句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须让矢岛自己说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 降矢那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早濑 你还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快去救城崎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总司令恩准了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次总算能干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为大哥报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽渡队长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种花招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 真崎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球体发生领域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干涉开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是设置球体时的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 扭曲空司的电磁波
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算用它中和我们的护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏这时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早濑 你去救城崎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 这里交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思前顾后不像你的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早濑还是单纯点好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本就没大脑 再考虑也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城崎起到你大脑的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须赶快找回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子正身陷危机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还犹豫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JUDA和御崎町有我们保护
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绘美就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 正义的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也找矢岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着瞧吧 两根角的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保护浩一的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤 久嵩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城崎绘美…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未抵达这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎和矢岛中途绕道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们边谈边等他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉对你动粗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤久嵩会来这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 把你交给总司令前有话要问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你喜欢浩一吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是俄罗斯的核潜艇基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经被加藤机关接收
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界都是我们的好朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于城崎绘美的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信你最了解矢岛英明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们对矢岛做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时没有因子的APARESHION
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即找到了新的因子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有幸被选中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是回收了他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,APARESHION的D-SOIL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有LINEBARREL那样卓越的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全复活需要花费时日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是矢岛干的那些事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试问早濑浩一同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被LINEBARREL复活后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前判若两人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你喜欢浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才留在他身边的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法回答吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢还缠着他?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单纯把他作为LINEBARREL的因子利用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙骗浩一让他上战场卖命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的我自己也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总在浩一身边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排斥理沙子让她伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不喜欢浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还穿上这种衣服给她们看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样很开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前劝你来我这边时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以矢岛的事为理由拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在没有这个问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想邀请我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.68,0:12:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此一时彼一时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也应该明白了更多事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们的力量面前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界放弃了抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择虚假的和平 沉默了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中没有对未来的想像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只盼望维持现状闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫ELVIS吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘多拉魔盒底留下的“盲目的希望”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不搞什么征服世界的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平还会继续
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前电影里曾说过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“波鲁及亚家族30年的暴政
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育出米开朗基罗和达芬奇的文艺复兴”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“但瑞典500年的和平与民主又孕育出了什么呢”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“木偶钟而已”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育出想像需要的是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是压迫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盼望压迫中解脱会催生想像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最适合让人发挥想像的压迫是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸存者与死者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们明确划分开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将成为最大的压迫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人的生命是平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能称之为人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去想像力为活着而活着的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不过是服从程序的机械
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与MACHINA无异
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要做的是成为“人类”这台MACHINA的因子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为所有这一切的“杀人因子”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有想像力的MACHINA们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被我们这些因子淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有挣扎着想活下去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能察觉到作为人活下去的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是加藤机关的征服世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早濑浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想把握住真正的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就来加藤机关
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但希望你能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢他的话就离开浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留在浩一身边会有女孩伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早以前就想着浩一 为他努力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单纯一心一意的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再折磨她了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理沙子?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢理沙子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初怨恨自己的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会把这样的人选作因子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在是为了战斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护世界的使命?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法得出答案的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能亲自动手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不该继续留在浩一身边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护罩被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BARRET ARM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想前进一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缩小护罩范围2公里重新展开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家退后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算躲在护罩里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干掉那个大块头就没意义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这里顶住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到浩一回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我们重新展开护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要靠自己的力量誓死保卫这片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一和我都是正义的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会输给绘美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一真是个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小就喊着要当正义的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是被人欺负 所以我们都保护他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的早濑有能力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要保护你们不是理所应当的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理沙子 暂时留在这里看着早濑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的人类是无力的MACHINA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必豁出性命保护那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也许不会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢怒不敢言的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为微不足道的梦想忍辱负重的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在有抗争的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这的确是城崎带给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非自己争取到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的正义也许是不值一提的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是想成为真正的正义使者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记茱迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.23,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会忘记石神大叔的诚恳请求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许多弱小的人就像我以前那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有信任我支持我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你会死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和遍布整个世界的"MACHINA"们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把城崎绘美带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按您的指示 收容在地下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但已经没有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早濑 带着她回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走地下通道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愉快的谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次战场上见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三丁目的护罩消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从天津大道到坂井重新展开护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御崎的特自部队后退至站前区域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好的不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明早濑浩一确实超越了想像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划能缩短两个步骤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了浩一他们才接受了那种命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放他们俩人回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有任何改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样对你更好不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早濑浩一和城崎绘美如果进展顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你收留了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我并没有成为你的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:21:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不利己 专门利人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人想起你 你也只为世界而活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后也为它而死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢岛说的?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早濑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早濑对理沙子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢岛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.94,0:23:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城崎身上的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.02,0:23:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是矢岛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人独处时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.12,0:23:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.62,0:23:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈上了成年人的阶梯?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.89,0:23:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.89,0:23:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说也算我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.96,0:23:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 最差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
